that suggested that there was
a lot more going on and by

00:17:54.990 --> 00:17:59.590
that I didn't really suggest that
it would come from me necessarily.

00:17:59.590 --> 00:18:01.490
I was hoping that people
would read the story

00:18:01.490 --> 00:18:06.350
and they would perhaps take
the challenge to finish it.

00:18:06.350 --> 00:18:11.070
&gt;&gt; Okay, I should point
out that I'm asking this

00:18:11.070 --> 00:18:14.310
because although I would
normally be interested,

00:18:14.310 --> 00:18:19.990
also there's an investigation
right now currently in South Africa

00:18:19.990 --> 00:18:24.510
into the treatment of
mentally ill patients.

00:18:24.510 --> 00:18:27.910
They were removed, a large
number of them were removed

00:18:27.910 --> 00:18:32.270
from their hospitals and they
were just sent elsewhere and many

00:18:32.270 --> 00:18:36.760
of them, or most of them
died and so it's a political

00:18:36.760 --> 00:18:40.960
and a social issue
and it's a tragedy.

00:18:40.960 --> 00:18:44.030
And so, since you're
writing about mental illness,

00:18:44.030 --> 00:18:49.060
I'm wondering if this
is more material for you

00:18:49.060 --> 00:18:54.390
for the stories that you write.

00:18:54.390 --> 00:19:02.110 position:56%
&gt;&gt; I mean, because I wrote the story
and I've spent about possibly close

00:19:02.110 --> 00:19:05.990
to a year talking about mental
illness in South Africa and talking

00:19:05.990 --> 00:19:11.200 position:56%
about the story specifically I mean,
when the news of that tragedy broke

00:19:11.200 --> 00:19:17.810
out it was heartbreaking and
then there was a thing they do

00:19:17.810 --> 00:19:22.130
in Parliament in South Africa where
the president addresses the nation

00:19:22.130 --> 00:19:26.130
and one of the people from the
political parties, the opposition,

00:19:26.130 --> 00:19:29.870
asked if they could give a
moment of silence to I think

00:19:29.870 --> 00:19:33.940
at that time it was around
125 people that had died,

00:19:33.940 --> 00:19:41.490 position:56%
and the Madam Speaker of
Parliament refused and she was like,

00:19:41.490 --> 00:19:47.060
we are not here to mourn 125 dead
people, so it was heartbreaking

00:19:47.060 --> 00:19:52.140
for me because at that
moment I really got to kind

00:19:52.140 --> 00:19:53.820
of understand what it means

00:19:53.820 --> 00:19:59.530
to have a family member whose got
mental illness and what it means

00:19:59.530 --> 00:20:03.040
when they die that the
government doesn't care.

00:20:03.040 --> 00:20:05.780
So because of how emotional
that was for me,

00:20:05.780 --> 00:20:10.240
I've never really seen it as,
to put it in a very crass way,

00:20:10.240 --> 00:20:12.330
as an opportunity for material.

00:20:12.330 --> 00:20:16.870
It's just been really heartbreaking
that I haven't even though

00:20:16.870 --> 00:20:22.150 position:56%
about do I write more about it or
do I make images or do I make forms?

00:20:22.150 --> 00:20:25.390
I haven't really thought about it.

00:20:28.130 --> 00:20:32.640
&gt;&gt; Well, let me ask you
