00:34:56.960 --> 00:35:00.200
of African literature and sort
of like what is being published

00:35:00.200 --> 00:35:01.650
and what people are reading.

00:35:01.650 --> 00:35:06.110
I don't necessarily think
that we as African writers

00:35:06.110 --> 00:35:08.510
or African publishers have
to do anything different.

00:35:08.510 --> 00:35:13.160
I mean, people are publishing
books, people are publishing online

00:35:13.160 --> 00:35:15.670
so for me the thing is if
you are really interested

00:35:15.670 --> 00:35:19.260
in reading any African
writer you will find them

00:35:19.260 --> 00:35:20.840
and there's a lot going on,

00:35:20.840 --> 00:35:22.880
and if you are really
interested you will find them

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:25.180
