00:41:46.190 --> 00:41:48.310
&gt;&gt; I mean, I completely get
you so even in South Africa,

00:41:48.310 --> 00:41:51.110
there's a bit of that
especially with depression.

00:41:51.110 --> 00:41:55.260
Parents will just tell you go play
outside, listen to some music,

00:41:55.260 --> 00:42:01.290
or watch movies as if that helps
so definitely there's a lot more

00:42:03.700 --> 00:42:08.490
and this is why I think I mean, the
story has been interesting for me

00:42:08.490 --> 00:42:10.260
because a lot of the conversations
about it have been from the point

00:42:10.260 --> 00:42:11.560
of the villages and their
traditional living there

00:42:11.560 --> 00:42:13.380
but the truth of it is that even
in the city there's a huge problem.

00:42:13.380 --> 00:42:14.940
&gt;&gt; You mentioned that you hadn't
written fiction before the short

00:42:14.940 --> 00:42:16.240
story and so I was going

00:42:16.240 --> 00:42:17.540
