00:42:25.070 --> 00:42:28.550
&gt;&gt; I mean I'm thinking
about it because even

00:42:28.550 --> 00:42:31.610
in my non-fiction I make
things up so [laughter] I mean,

00:42:31.610 --> 00:42:39.140
I think that the major
difference is really in facts.

00:42:39.140 --> 00:42:42.250
There's a certain level
with non-fiction

00:42:42.250 --> 00:42:48.390
that you really cannot write
that far away from the truth

00:42:48.390 --> 00:42:53.380
but with fiction you
can totally do that.

00:42:53.380 --> 00:42:58.830
For me it's all the same because
my poetry exists both in fiction

00:42:58.830 --> 00:43:03.070
and non-fiction, the real
difference is really in the facts.

00:43:10.460 --> 00:43:15.810
&gt;&gt; A couple of questions, how would
